  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 -\u00a0 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't want to make false promises - Leader of Opposition Sajith told empty-faced protesters",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "There is no major difference between the programs presented by the protesting parties and our programs.",
        "However, Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa said, \"I don't want to make a false promise that we will be able to form a government for a certain period of time and thereby solve the economic crisis.\"",
        "He made this known during a meeting with the Khali protestors on Monday (18) while further stating,",
        "There is no major difference between the programs presented by the protesting parties and our programs.",
        "But I look at the matter from a different angle when it is urged to specify the period for the formation of the interim government.",
        "An interim government should be formed with a program. Implementation of those programs should be the goal of the interim government.",
        "So if an interim government is formed for a certain period, if it is not able to complete the programs within that period, that government will also fail.",
        "It is doubtful to what extent the consensus achieved in the public sphere can be achieved in Parliament.",
        "The country has reached an economic crisis. In such a situation I cannot make false promise that people will get relief at once.",
        "However, steps will be taken to fulfill basic needs. An economy that has reached a critical condition should be built up gradually. Financial strength is also necessary to provide justice to people.",
        "We are in very difficult times. Similarly, banking structures have also been affected. We have thoroughly evaluated all the issues. So there is hope that the economy can be built despite the difficult situation, he said.",
        "It is noteworthy that the protestors who expressed their opinion during this time said that their struggle will continue if Ranil Wickremesinghe becomes the President and that the opposition parties should take all measures in the Parliament to defeat him."
      ],
